Template: face-authd/configure_pam
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Automatically configure PAM for face-authd?
 If enabled, the installer will insert a managed pam_face_auth.so block into:
  - /etc/pam.d/sudo
  - /etc/pam.d/gdm-password (if present)
 .
 Existing files are backed up once with a .bak.face-authd suffix.
